<text top="403" left="142" width="343" height="9" font="0">In  its  resolution  25/7,  the  Human  Rights  Council  requested  the  Special  Rapporteur </text>
<text top="415" left="113" width="371" height="9" font="0">on  the  promotion  and  protection  of  human  rights  and  fundamental  freedoms  while </text>
<text top="427" left="113" width="371" height="9" font="0">countering terrorism to report regularly to the Council and to present his reports, bearing in </text>
<text top="439" left="113" width="371" height="9" font="0">mind the content of that resolution, in conformity with its annual programme of work. The </text>
<text top="451" left="113" width="371" height="9" font="0">Special Rapporteur was due to submit his annual report to the Council at its twenty-eighth </text>
<text top="463" left="113" width="99" height="9" font="0">session (A/HRC/28/67). </text>
<text top="481" left="142" width="342" height="9" font="0">At the request of the mandate holder, the Special Rapporteur will submit his annual </text>
